products.name: AMD - Ryzen 5 1600 Six-Core 3.2 GHz Desktop Processor
products.longDescription: Bank on solid, efficient computing performance with this six-core AMD Ryzen 5 desktop processor. Its 3.6GHz maximum turbo core speed sufficiently supports 1080p and VR gaming, and its 16MB L3 cache memory provides an enhanced CPU memory operation. The 65W default thermal design power of this AMD Ryzen 5 desktop processor lets you build a power-efficient computer system.

products.name: Intel - Core i3-8100 Coffee Lake Quad-Core 3.6 GHz Desktop Processor - Silver
products.longDescription: Increase productivity with this eighth-generation Intel Core i3 processor. Its low power consumption at 65W keeps motherboard components cool, and its 3.60GHz clock speed lets you multitask efficiently on each of the four cores. This Intel Core i3 processor supports up to 64GB of DDR4 RAM to meet future expansion needs.

products.name: Intel - Core i7-8700 Coffee Lake Six-Core 3.2 GHz Desktop Processor
products.longDescription: Construct a lightning-fast motherboard with this six-core Intel Core i7 processor. Its 12MB of cache provides fast data retrieval to speed up operations, and its low 65W power consumption keeps components cool. Crank this eighth-generation Intel Core i7 processor up to its turbo frequency of 4.6GHz to run large programs.

products.name: Intel - Core i7-8700K Coffee Lake Six-Core 3.7 GHz Desktop Processor
products.longDescription: Use this Intel Core i7 processor to upgrade your current motherboard. Its 3.7GHz base frequency can be overclocked to 4.7GHz for running multiple power-hungry programs over its six cores, and it supports 4K graphics for enjoying movies and games. This Intel Core i7 processor lets you add up to 64GB of DDR4 RAM for powerful multitasking.

products.name: Intel - Core i5-8600K Coffee Lake Six-Core 3.6 GHz Desktop Processor - Silver
products.longDescription: Build your own computer beginning with this Intel Core i5 processor. Its 9MB of cache memory offers fast data retrieval for maximum efficiency, and the base frequency of 3.6GHz powers through demanding applications and programs. Switch between multiple tasks smoothly with this eighth-generation Intel Core i5 processor when you pair it with up to 64GB of DDR4 RAM.

products.name: Intel - Core i5-8400 Coffee Lake Six-Core 2.8 GHz Desktop Processor - Silver
products.longDescription: Supercharge your custom PC with this eighth-generation Intel Core i5 processor. products.name: AMD - Ryzen 5 2400G Quad-Core 3.6 GHz Desktop Processor

This AMD Ryzen 5 processor supports PCIe 3.0 and HDMI to interface with up-to-date hardware and displays.

This AMD Ryzen 7 processor has eight cores for completing multiple system-intensive tasks at once.
